claim.claim-text:
1. A vehicle for storing and transporting cargo comprising: 
a cargo box for supporting and storing the cargo in said vehicle, said cargo box defined by a generally planar cargo floor extending a front end and a rear open end and a pair of spaced apart and generally parallel side walls extending between said front end and said rear open end along opposing sides of said cargo floor; 
a tailgate operatively connected to said rear open end of said cargo floor and pivotal between an open position extending from said cargo floor and generally planar therewith for providing access to said cargo box and a closed position extending generally upright from said rear open end of said cargo floor between said opposing side walls for closing said cargo box; said tailgate including a cavity recessed within said tailgate and a door for closing said cavity in said tailgate.
